      "content": "it just feels like everything is getting so heavy lately. my joints ache every single day and i can't even make tea without someone having to come help me. i look at my kids and i see how tired they are from looking after me... i hate being such a nuisance. i just wish i could find some peace and not be a weight on everyone else anymore.",
